Once it strikes,
it will not stop
draining energy from the victim
even if it gets
too heavy to fly.

Once it strikes,

It attacks in a
stealthy manner,
without warning. Its sharp fangs
are used to bite
and suck blood.

However hard its
victim's hide may
be, it punctures with sharp fangs
and gorges itself
with blood.

It can drink more
than 10 ounces of
blood at once. If it has too much,
it gets heavy and
flies clumsily.

When it plunges
its fangs into its
prey, it instantly draws and gulps
down more than ten
ounces of blood.

GOLBAT loves to drink the blood of
living things. It is particularly active
in the pitch black of night. This POKMON flits around in the night
skies, seeking fresh blood.

GOLBAT bites down on prey with its four
fangs and drinks the victims blood.
It becomes active on inky dark moonless nights, flying around to
attack people and POKMON.

Its fangs easily puncture even thick
animal hide. It loves to feast on the blood
of people and POKMON. It flits about in
darkness and strikes from behind.

It clamps down on its prey with needle-
sharp fangs and drains over 10 ounces of
blood in one gulp.

Once it bites, it will not stop draining
energy from the victim even if it gets too
heavy to fly.

It loves the blood of humans and
Pokmon. It flies around at night
in search of neck veins.

Once it starts sucking blood, it
does not stop until it is full. It
flies at night in search of prey.

Its sharp fangs puncture the
toughest of hides and have small
holes for greedily sucking blood.

Dieses Pokmon saugt dem Gegner selbst dann noch

Cuando ataque, seguir chupando energa de su

Quando attacca, non smette di succhiare lenergia

Quand il se met  sucer du sang, il ne sarrte
quune fois rassasi. Cest un chasseur nocturne.

Hat es einmal angefangen Blut zu saugen, hrt es
erst wieder auf, wenn es satt ist. Es jagt nachts.

Cuando chupa sangre, no para hasta hartarse.
Por la noche sale volando a la caza de presas.

Quando inizia a succhiare sangue, non smette finch
non  sazio. Vola di notte in cerca di prede.

Nosferalto adore boire le sang des cratures vivantes.
Il est particulirement actif pendant les nuits noires.
Ce Pokmon se balade dans les cieux toils,  la recherche
de sang frais.

Golbat hat es auf das Blut von Lebewesen abgesehen.
Im Schutze der Nacht wird es besonders aktiv. Dieses
Pokmon fliegt durch die Nacht, um nach frischem Blut
zu suchen.

A Golbat le encanta chuparles la sangre a los seres vivos. Este
Pokmon es ms activo en la oscuridad de la noche. Es al caer
la noche cuando sale a revolotear y a buscar sangre fresca.

Golbat adora bere il sangue di creature viventi.
 particolarmente attivo di notte, nella totale oscurit.
Svolazza nel cielo notturno in cerca di sangue fresco.

Golbat loves to drink the blood of living things. It is particularly
active in the pitch black of night. This Pokmon flits around in
the night skies, seeking fresh blood.

Nosferalto mord sa proie grce  ses quatre crocs pour
boire son sang. Il ne sort que lorsque la nuit est noire
et sans lune, pour voleter en qute de gens et de Pokmon
 mordre.

Golbat beit seine Beute mit seinen vier Reizhnen und trinkt
das Blut seiner Opfer. Es wird in Nchten aktiv, in denen nicht
einmal der Mond scheint. Es fliegt dann durch die Dunkelheit
und greift Menschen und Pokmon an.

Golbat derriba a sus vctimas mordindoles con los cuatro
colmillos que tiene y chupndoles la sangre. Solo entra en
accin en las noches sin luna. Revolotea en la oscuridad para
atacar a Pokmon y personas.

Golbat azzanna i nemici con i suoi quattro canini e ne beve
il sangue.  particolarmente attivo nel buio pesto delle notti
senza luna e vola attaccando le persone e gli altri Pokmon.

Golbat bites down on prey with its four fangs and drinks
the victims blood. It becomes active on inky dark
moonless nights, flying around to attack people and Pokmon.

Ses crocs sont creux comme des pailles et
tonnamment fragiles. Ils sont en revanche
parfaits pour sucer le sang de ses victimes.

Seine dicken Reizhne sind im Inneren hohl
wie Strohhalme und zerbrechlich. Sie sind das
Produkt seiner Entwicklung zum Blutsauger.

Succiona la sangre de sus presas con sus
gruesos colmillos, que son huecos por dentro a
modo de caa y ms frgiles de lo que parecen.

I suoi grossi canini sono cavi come cannucce
e sorprendentemente fragili. Se ne serve per
succhiare il sangue.

Its thick fangs are hollow like straws, making
them unexpectedly fragile. These fangs are
specialized for sucking blood.

Il arrive quun Nosferalto ayant trop suc de
sang ne puisse plus voler et tombe au sol,
o il est dvor par dautres Pokmon.

Manchmal saugt es so viel Blut, dass es
hilflos zu Boden fllt und leichte Beute fr
andere Pokmon wird.

A veces chupa tanta sangre que es incapaz de
volar y cae al suelo para acabar siendo presa
de otros Pokmon.

Se succhia troppo sangue, non riesce pi
a volare e cade a terra diventando preda
di altri Pokmon.

Sometimes they drink so much blood, they cant
fly anymore. Then they fall to the ground and
become food for other Pokmon.

On rencontre parfois des Nosferalto dents
que la faim a pousss  attaquer un Pokmon
de type Acier.

Um seinen Hunger zu stillen, versucht es
mitunter auch, in Stahl-Pokmon zu beien,
und bricht sich dabei die Reizhne ab.

En ocasiones se ven ejemplares a los que les
falta algn colmillo por haber intentado morder
a un Pokmon de tipo Acero, presas del hambre.

A volte si vedono dei Golbat senza canini
perch, spinti dalla fame, hanno provato
ad azzannare un Pokmon di tipo Acciaio.

Every once in a while, youll see a Golbat thats
missing some fangs. This happens when hunger
drives it to try biting a Steel-type Pokmon.

Ce Pokmon peut absorber jusqu 300 ml
de sang dun coup. Victime de sa gourmandise,
il en devient parfois trop lourd pour voler.

In einem Schluck kann es bis zu 300 ml Blut
absaugen. Manchmal trinkt es so viel, dass es
nicht mehr fliegen kann.

Es capaz de ingerir 300 cc de sangre de una
sentada. A veces chupa tanta que es incapaz
de volar.

Pu succhiare 300 cc di sangue in un colpo
solo. Quando ne succhia troppo, non riesce
pi a volare.

They can suck down over 10 ounces of blood in
one go. They have been known to drink so much
blood that they can no longer fly.

Il sapproche furtivement et attaque sans crier
gare. Ses crocs acrs lui servent  sucer le sang.

Golbat nhert sich schnell und lautlos an.
Mit seinen spitzen Zhnen beit es zu und
saugt seinen Opfern Blut ab.

Tras aproximarse sigilosamente a su objetivo,
utiliza sus afilados colmillos para chuparle la
sangre.

Attacca in modo repentino e furtivo. Usa i denti
aguzzi per mordere e succhiare sangue.
